<section>
	<h2>Purpose</h2>
	<p class="alert alert-info">Style special relationship between cell, vector (row/col) and group (tbody/colgroup). It also simulate a column hovering effect for table.</p>

	<p>Please note: The zebra stripping that is an alternate row styled are out of scope of this plugin. Regarding that specific effect, please consult the twitter bootstrap CSS documentations.</p>
	
</section>

<section>
	<h2>Use when</h2>
	<ul>
		<li>To style special relationship in table</li>
		<li>To provide a column hovering effect to the user, when appropriate</li>
	</ul>
</section>

<section>
	<h2>Do not use when</h2>
	<ul>
		<li>For styling table that are not conform at the 12 technique for tables</li>
	</ul>
</section>


